Author: Sunopsis Version: 4.0 Last Update : DEC-2004
Description : - Reverse Knowledge Module - Reverse engineering Knowledge Module to retrieve the tables for Informix SE databases
To use this knowledge module and run the reverse engineering: 1. Import this knowledge module in one of your projects. 2. Create an Informix SE technology model and choose the reverse context as well as the knowledge module in the "reverse" tab. 3. Execute the reverse engineering and follow up the steps in the logs.
Restrictions: - The mask of tables to reverse must not be empty, and at least contain the '%' character. - The tab Selective reverse cannot be used with this knowledge module.

create table SNP_REV_CTEMP ( I_MOD <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_NUMERIC","10")?> NOT NULL, TABLE_NAME <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","100")?> NOT NULL, COL_NAME <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","100")?> NOT NULL, COL_HEADING <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","35")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, COL_DESC <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","250")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, DT_DRIVER <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_NUMERIC","10")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, POS <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_NUMERIC","10")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, LONGC <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_NUMERIC","10")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, SCALEC <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_NUMERIC","10")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, FILE_POS <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_NUMERIC","10")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, BYTES <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_NUMERIC","10")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, IND_WRITE <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","1")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, COL_MANDATORY <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","1")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, CHECK_FLOW <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","1")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, CHECK_STAT <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","1")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, COL_FORMAT <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","35")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, COL_DEC_SEP <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","1")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, REC_CODE_LIST <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","250")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, COL_NULL_IF_ERR <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","1")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?>, DEF_VALUE <?=snpRef.getDataType("SRC_VARCHAR","100")?> <?=snpRef.getInfo("SRC_DDL_NULL")?> )
insert into SNP_REV_TABLE ( I_MOD, TABLE_NAME, RES_NAME, TABLE_ALIAS, TABLE_TYPE, IND_SHOW, R_COUNT ) values ( <%=snpRef.getModel("ID")%>, :TABLE_NAME, :RES_NAME, :TABLE_ALIAS, 'T', '1', :R_COUNT )

select t.tabname TABLE_NAME, trim(t.tabname) RES_NAME, t.tabname[1,3] TABLE_ALIAS, t.nrows R_COUNT from informix.systables t where t.owner = '<%=snpRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and t.tabname like '<%=snpRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' and t.tabtype in ( 'T','V','E')

insert into SNP_REV_CTEMP ( I_MOD, TABLE_NAME, COL_NAME, DT_DRIVER, POS, LONGC, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW ) values ( <%=snpRef.getModel("ID")%>, :TABLE_NAME, :COL_NAME, :DT_DRIVER, :POS, :LONGC, '1', '1' )

select t.tabname TABLE_NAME, c.colname COL_NAME, coltype DT_DRIVER, c.colno POS, c.collength LONGC from informix.syscolumns c, informix.systables t Where t.owner like '<%=snpRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and (t.tabname like '<%=snpRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>' ) and (t.tabid = c.tabid)

insert into SNP_REV_COL ( I_MOD, TABLE_NAME, COL_NAME, DT_DRIVER, POS, LONGC, BYTES, SCALEC, COL_MANDATORY, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW ) select c.i_mod I_MOD, c.table_name TABLE_NAME, c.col_name COL_NAME, case when c.dt_driver >= 256 then case when c.dt_driver - 256=0 then 'CHAR' when c.dt_driver - 256=1 then 'SMALLINT' when c.dt_driver - 256=2 then 'INTEGER' when c.dt_driver - 256=3 then 'FLOAT' when c.dt_driver - 256=4 then 'SMALLFLOAT' when c.dt_driver - 256=5 then 'DECIMAL' when c.dt_driver - 256=6 then 'SERIAL' when c.dt_driver - 256=7 then 'DATE' when c.dt_driver - 256=8 then 'MONEY' when c.dt_driver - 256=10 then 'DATETIME' when c.dt_driver - 256=11 then 'BYTE' when c.dt_driver - 256=12 then 'TEXT' when c.dt_driver - 256=13 then 'VARCHAR' when c.dt_driver - 256=14 then 'INTERVAL' when c.dt_driver - 256=15 then 'NCHAR' when c.dt_driver - 256=16 then 'NVCHAR' end when c.dt_driver < 256 then case when c.dt_driver =0 then 'CHAR' when c.dt_driver =1 then 'SMALLINT' when c.dt_driver =2 then 'INTEGER' when c.dt_driver =3 then 'FLOAT' when c.dt_driver =4 then 'SMALLFLOAT' when c.dt_driver =5 then 'DECIMAL' when c.dt_driver =6 then 'SERIAL' when c.dt_driver =7 then 'DATE' when c.dt_driver =8 then 'MONEY' when c.dt_driver =10 then 'DATETIME' when c.dt_driver =11 then 'BYTE' when c.dt_driver =12 then 'TEXT' when c.dt_driver =13 then 'VARCHAR' when c.dt_driver =14 then 'INTERVAL' when c.dt_driver =15 then 'NCHAR' when c.dt_driver =16 then 'NVCHAR' end end, c.pos POS, case when c.dt_driver >=256 then case when c.dt_driver-256 = 0 then longc when c.dt_driver-256 = 1 then 5 when (c.dt_driver-256 = 2 or c.dt_driver-256 = 6) then 10 when c.dt_driver-256 = 3 then 64 when c.dt_driver-256 = 4 then 32 when (c.dt_driver-256 = 5 or c.dt_driver = 8) then ((longc / 256)) when (c.dt_driver-256 = 13 or c.dt_driver-256 = 16) then (longc - ((longc / 256))*256) end when c.dt_driver <256 then case when c.dt_driver = 0 then longc when c.dt_driver = 1 then 5 when (c.dt_driver = 2 or c.dt_driver = 6) then 10 when c.dt_driver = 3 then 64 when c.dt_driver = 4 then 32 when (c.dt_driver = 5 or c.dt_driver = 8) then ((longc / 256)) when (c.dt_driver = 13 or c.dt_driver = 16) then (longc - ((longc / 256))*256) end end LONGC, case when c.dt_driver >=256 then case when c.dt_driver-256 = 0 then longc when c.dt_driver-256 = 1 then 5 when (c.dt_driver-256 = 2 or c.dt_driver-256 = 6) then 10 when c.dt_driver-256 = 3 then 64 when c.dt_driver-256 = 4 then 32 when (c.dt_driver-256 = 5 or c.dt_driver = 8) then ((longc / 256)) when (c.dt_driver-256 = 13 or c.dt_driver-256 = 16) then (longc - ((longc / 256))*256) end when c.dt_driver <256 then case when c.dt_driver = 0 then longc when c.dt_driver = 1 then 5 when (c.dt_driver = 2 or c.dt_driver = 6) then 10 when c.dt_driver = 3 then 64 when c.dt_driver = 4 then 32 when (c.dt_driver = 5 or c.dt_driver = 8) then ((longc / 256)) when (c.dt_driver = 13 or c.dt_driver = 16) then (longc - ((longc / 256))*256) end end, case when c.dt_driver >=256 then case when (c.dt_driver-256 = 1 or c.dt_driver-256 = 2 or c.dt_driver-256 = 6) then 0 when (c.dt_driver-256 = 5 or c.dt_driver-256 = 8) then (c.longc - (((c.longc / 256))*256)) end when c.dt_driver <256 then case when (c.dt_driver = 1 or c.dt_driver = 2 or c.dt_driver = 6) then 0 when (c.dt_driver = 5 or c.dt_driver = 8) then (c.longc - (((c.longc / 256))*256)) end end SCALEC, case when c.dt_driver >= 256 then '1' ELSE '0' end, CHECK_STAT, CHECK_FLOW from snp_rev_ctemp c
insert into SNP_REV_KEY ( I_MOD, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, CONS_TYPE, IND_ACTIVE, CHECK_FLOW, CHECK_STAT ) values ( <%=snpRef.getModel("ID")%>, :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, 'PK', '1', '1', '1' )

select tab.tabname TABLE_NAME, idx.idxname KEY_NAME from informix.sysindexes idx, informix.systables tab where idx.idxtype = 'U' and idx.tabid = tab.tabid and tab.owner = '<%=snpRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and tab.tabname like '<%=snpRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'
insert into SNP_REV_KEY_COL ( I_MOD, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, COL_NAME, POS ) values ( <%=snpRef.getModel("ID")%>, :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, :COL_NAME, :POS )

select tab.tabname TABLE_NAME, idx.idxname KEY_NAME, col.colname COL_NAME, col.colno POS from informix.sysindexes idx, informix.systables tab, informix.syscolumns col where idx.tabid = tab.tabid and idx.idxtype in ('U') and ( (col.colno = idx.part1 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part2 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part3 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part4 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part5 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part6 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part7 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part8 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) ) and tab.owner = '<%=snpRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and tab.tabname like '<%=snpRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'
insert into SNP_REV_KEY ( I_MOD, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, CONS_TYPE, IND_ACTIVE, CHECK_FLOW, CHECK_STAT ) values ( <%=snpRef.getModel("ID")%>, :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, 'I', '1', '1', '1' )

select tab.tabname TABLE_NAME, idx.idxname KEY_NAME from informix.sysindexes idx, informix.systables tab where idx.idxtype = 'D' and idx.tabid = tab.tabid and tab.owner = '<%=snpRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and tab.tabname like '<%=snpRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'
insert into SNP_REV_KEY_COL ( I_MOD, TABLE_NAME, KEY_NAME, COL_NAME, POS ) values ( <%=snpRef.getModel("ID")%>, :TABLE_NAME, :KEY_NAME, :COL_NAME, :POS )

select tab.tabname TABLE_NAME, idx.idxname KEY_NAME, col.colname COL_NAME, col.colno POS from informix.sysindexes idx, informix.systables tab, informix.syscolumns col where idx.tabid = tab.tabid and idx.idxtype in ('D') and ( (col.colno = idx.part1 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part2 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part3 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part4 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part5 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part6 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part7 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) or (col.colno = idx.part8 and col.tabid = idx.tabid) ) and tab.owner = '<%=snpRef.getModel("SCHEMA_NAME")%>' and tab.tabname like '<%=snpRef.getModel("REV_OBJ_PATT")%>'
update snp_rev_table set res_name = rtrim(res_name), table_name = rtrim(table_name)
update snp_rev_col set dt_driver = rtrim(dt_driver), col_name = rtrim(col_name), table_name = rtrim(table_name)
update snp_rev_key set key_name = rtrim(key_name), table_name = rtrim(table_name)
update snp_rev_key_col set key_name = rtrim(key_name), table_name = rtrim(table_name), col_name = rtrim(col_name)
